metadata.name: L1 Nanobot
metadata.description: L1 Lab Item used for transforming your OBYC Bear into into a L1 Machine Bear. The OBYC Hazmat Division consists of 10,000 Lab Items with 7,777 L1 Lab Items being airdropped to all Okay Bear Yacht Club Bears. Choose your path wisely with L2 Lab Items mint. The official snapshot was taken on 9/19/2022 at 9:19 PM EST.
